<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 22:03:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>爱尔兰新总理表示距离承认巴勒斯坦国“更近了”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/new-irish-pm-says-getting-much-closer-to-recognising-palestinian-state/articleshow/109255552.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255552.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/new-irish-pm-says-getting-much-closer-to-recognising-palestinian-state/articleshow/109255552.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国称地中海船只倾覆 45 名移民失踪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-says-45-migrants-missing-after-boat-capsizes-in-mediterranean/articleshow/109255465.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255465.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;意大利海岸警卫队周三表示，在另一起沉船事故中，已发现 9 具遇难者尸体，并救起 22 人，其中 15 人疑似失踪。幸存者被带到附近的意大利兰佩杜萨岛，这是许多寻求到达欧盟的移民的第一个停靠港。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-says-45-migrants-missing-after-boat-capsizes-in-mediterranean/articleshow/109255465.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯因部长“不可接受”言论召见法国大使</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-summons-french-ambassador-over-ministers-unacceptable-comments/articleshow/109255410.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255410.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-summons-french-ambassador-over-ministers-unacceptable-comments/articleshow/109255410.cms</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，到 2050 年，日本独居老年人口将增加 47%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-elderly-population-living-alone-to-jump-47-by-2050-research/articleshow/109254665.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109254665.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-elderly-population-living-alone-to-jump-47-by-2050-research/articleshow/109254665.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击威胁使该地区紧张，以色列袭击加沙</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-pounds-gaza-as-iran-attack-threat-puts-region-on-edge/articleshow/109254496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109254496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;居民报告周五以色列在加沙中部猛烈开火，伊朗威胁要对本月在叙利亚发动的袭击造成两名伊朗将军死亡，导致地区紧张局势加剧。哈马斯统治地区当局报告称，加沙中部地区发生了数十次新的空袭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-pounds-gaza-as-iran-attack-threat-puts-region-on-edge/articleshow/109254496.cms</guid></item><item><title>白宫称伊朗对以色列的威胁“真实”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-threat-to-israel-real-says-white-house/articleshow/109253312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109253312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;白宫承认伊朗在叙利亚袭击后对以色列发出威胁。柯比确保防御准备状态。阿亚图拉发誓要进行惩罚，内塔尼亚胡则表示已做好准备。德黑兰批评联合国保持沉默，内塔尼亚胡誓言进行报复。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-threat-to-israel-real-says-white-house/articleshow/109253312.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙家庭 60 多名成员在以色列多次袭击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109253253.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109253253.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙的塔巴蒂比一家在不到一个月的时间里第二次陷入哀悼，此前以色列对他们避难的建筑物进行了多次轰炸，造成 60 多名亲属死亡。 - “我们在里面时”房屋遭到轰炸 - 塔巴蒂比一家多次因以色列的轰炸而流离失所，他们已经陷入了哀悼之中。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109253253.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国专家谴责巴基斯坦强迫婚姻和少数群体改变宗教信仰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/un-experts-condemn-forced-marriages-religious-conversions-of-minorities-in-pakistan/articleshow/109252208.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109252208.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国专家周四表示，巴基斯坦宗教少数群体的妇女和儿童很容易遭受强迫宗教皈依和婚姻，以及性侵犯和贩运。声明还敦促巴基斯坦当局平等对待所有妇女，包括来自“印度教和基督教”社区的妇女。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:39:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/un-experts-condemn-forced-marriages-religious-conversions-of-minorities-in-pakistan/articleshow/109252208.cms</guid></item><item><title>意大利将在黎巴嫩、科特迪瓦和埃塞俄比亚招募移民工人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-to-recruit-migrant-workers-in-lebanon-ivory-coast-and-ethiopia/articleshow/109254388.cms</link><description>意大利同意通过天主教慈善机构圣艾智德社区牵头的一项特别倡议，欢迎来自黎巴嫩、科特迪瓦和埃塞俄比亚的 300 名移民工人。这些人不会获得难民身份，但将成为名为“工作走廊”的试点项目的一部分。这项倡议得到了内政部的批准，符合总理乔治亚·梅洛尼政府的立场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-to-recruit-migrant-workers-in-lebanon-ivory-coast-and-ethiopia/articleshow/109254388.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国外交部将巴基斯坦列入“太危险而不能旅行”的国家名单</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/uk-foreign-office-adds-pakistan-to-its-list-of-countries-too-dangerous-to-travel/articleshow/109252405.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109252405.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国外交、联邦与发展办公室（FCDO）最近将巴基斯坦添加到其国家名单中，称其对英国公民旅行“太危险”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/uk-foreign-office-adds-pakistan-to-its-list-of-countries-too-dangerous-to-travel/articleshow/109252405.cms</guid></item><item><title>庞贝古城发现隐藏了 2000 年的引人注目的画作</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hidden-for-2000-years-striking-paintings-uncovered-in-pompeii/articleshow/109247650.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109247650.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;庞贝城最近的发掘发现了一个宴会厅，里面有神话壁画，包括阿波罗引诱卡桑德拉和特洛伊的海伦与巴黎会面的壁画。这个保存完好的遗址还设有面包店和马赛克地板，让您可以深入了解古罗马生活。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hidden-for-2000-years-striking-paintings-uncovered-in-pompeii/articleshow/109247650.cms</guid></item><item><title>“不需要手机信号塔：中国彻底改变了智能手机通信”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/no-need-for-cell-towers-china-has-revolutionised-smartphone-communications/articleshow/109246416.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109246416.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国科学家实现了突破性的里程碑，世界上第一颗卫星“天通”实现了智能手机直接通话。地球同步轨道天通一号系列覆盖亚太地区，支持华为、小米、荣耀、OPPO等品牌。卫星呼叫对于甘肃地震等紧急情况至关重要。中国在卫星通信领域处于领先地位，缩小了全球通信差距。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/no-need-for-cell-towers-china-has-revolutionised-smartphone-communications/articleshow/109246416.cms</guid></item><item><title>意大利水电站爆炸造成的死亡人数上升至7人，最后一批尸体已被找到</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/death-toll-from-italian-hydroelectric-plant-explosion-rises-to-7-as-the-last-bodies-are-recovered/articleshow/109244045.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109244045.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/death-toll-from-italian-hydroelectric-plant-explosion-rises-to-7-as-the-last-bodies-are-recovered/articleshow/109244045.cms</guid></item><item><title>抗衰老活动家因其脸部照片引发争议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/anti-ageing-activist-sparks-controversy-with-picture-of-his-face/articleshow/109243193.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109243193.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;布莱恩·约翰逊在社交媒体上发表的有关老龄化的帖子引发了批​​评。尽管遭到强烈反对，他还是对健康制度进行了投资。硅谷人物约翰逊在走向永葆青春的抗衰老之旅中面临伦理争议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:29:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/anti-ageing-activist-sparks-controversy-with-picture-of-his-face/articleshow/109243193.cms</guid></item><item><title>威廉王子在个人挑战中适应“在家办公”的王室职责</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-william-adapts-to-wfh-royal-duties-amid-personal-challenges/articleshow/109243679.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109243679.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;威廉王子将通过面对面和数字参与相结合的方式恢复全职王室职​​责，形成一种新的运营战略，这可能预示着他在未来统治期间的做法。这一决定是在他的妻子凯特·米德尔顿 (Kate Middleton) 被诊断出患有癌症后，公众知名度下降了一段时间后做出的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:28:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-william-adapts-to-wfh-royal-duties-amid-personal-challenges/articleshow/109243679.cms</guid></item><item><title>因“太友善”而被解雇的狗成为台湾地震救灾英雄</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dog-once-fired-for-being-too-friendly-becomes-hero-of-taiwans-earthquake-response/articleshow/109243346.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109243346.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dog-once-fired-for-being-too-friendly-becomes-hero-of-taiwans-earthquake-response/articleshow/109243346.cms</guid></item><item><title>由于担心神秘的“杀戮名单”，以色列和伊朗的紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-iran-tensions-rise-amid-fears-of-a-mystery-kill-list/articleshow/109243590.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109243590.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-iran-tensions-rise-amid-fears-of-a-mystery-kill-list/articleshow/109243590.cms</guid></item><item><title>威廉王子自妻子患癌症消息后首次露面</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-william-makes-first-appearance-since-wifes-cancer-announcement/articleshow/109242923.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109242923.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周四，自妻子凯特·米德尔顿确诊患有癌症以来，威廉王子首次公开露面。周四晚上，这位 41 岁的老人被拍到和他 10 岁的儿子乔治一起观看一场足球比赛，为他的球队阿斯顿维拉加油。凯特通过上个月发布的一段视频透露，她被诊断患有癌症，正在接受“预防性化疗”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-william-makes-first-appearance-since-wifes-cancer-announcement/articleshow/109242923.cms</guid></item><item><title>大规模袭击摧毁了乌克兰最大的发电厂之一</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/massive-attack-destroys-one-of-ukraines-largest-power-plants/articleshow/109241576.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109241576.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一次大规模导弹和无人机袭击摧毁了乌克兰重要的特里皮尔斯卡发电厂，对重要部件造成大面积损坏并引发大火。俄罗斯总统普京声称要进行报复。尽管该工厂目前由电网管理电力供应，但夏季的担忧依然存在。哈尔科夫的能源基础设施也受到影响，导致数千人无能为力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:23:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/massive-attack-destroys-one-of-ukraines-largest-power-plants/articleshow/109241576.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦机构：以色列军队在约旦河西岸造成两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-kill-2-in-west-bank-palestinian-agency/articleshow/109241360.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109241360.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军队在图巴斯开枪打死了两名巴勒斯坦人，其中一人在车内，另一人则在阿尔法拉难民营枪杀。图巴斯是约旦河西岸的热点地区，暴力事件不断增加。加沙冲突升级，哈马斯袭击以色列，造成双方重大人员伤亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:17:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-kill-2-in-west-bank-palestinian-agency/articleshow/109241360.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>